docs.text: Obsidian Notes ¶ Publish your public notes with MkDocs Hello World! ¶ The index.md in the /docs folder is the homepage you see here. The folders in /docs appear as the main sections on the navigation bar. The notes appear as pages within these sections. For example, Note 1 in Topic 1 First Test Page is the first Page I am going to link!
